{"type": "article", "id": 33461, "title": "LVMH 或将进军体育界，以及，上海时装周终于进入了尾声 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为您挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-10-19T02:45:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 330, "name": "可口可乐"}, {"id": 1029, "name": "Lego"}, {"id": 26358, "name": "A Bathing Ape"}, {"id": 33826, "name": "2016 上海时装周"}, {"id": 34089, "name": "英镑贬值"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 466, "name": "LVMH"}, {"id": 1330, "name": "ASOS"}, {"id": 2326, "name": "Gap"}, {"id": 8195, "name": "Banana Republic"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 34088, "name": "Reebook"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/201610191008285HLtQJjaSAZGBuTb.png", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/banana-republic-to-close-all-uk-stores\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Banana Republic 将关闭它在英国的所有门店</b></a> | 昨日，Banana Republic 宣布它将关闭在英国地区的八家门店。Banana Republic 八月的业绩同比下降了 9%，这是它连续六个月出现业绩下滑。此外，Banana Republic 还在把它位于纽约的门店转成特卖店的进程中。通过这些策略，Banana Republic 的母公司 Gap 集团计划在全球关闭近 75 家门店。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"https://www.businessoffashion.com/articles/news-analysis/asos-shares-slump-as-sales-growth-forecast-disappoints-investors\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>ASOS 不被投资者看好，股价下跌</b></a> | 尽管 2016 财年销售强劲，ASOS 预计在 2017 年能实现销售 20－25% 的增长。不过，Berenberg 的分析师 Michelle Wilson 在邮件中指出，ASOS 的扩张是基于低价策略和它在全球业务上的投资，并非没有风险。昨日，ASOS 的股价下跌了 7.7%，目前市值约为 50 亿美元，这也是在 6 月 24 日单日股价下跌 9% 之后，又一次大幅下跌。&nbsp;</p><p><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-10-18/italian-bicycle-maker-pinarello-says-it-s-been-reviewing-options\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>LVMH 集团或将收购意大利高档自行车品牌 Pinarello</b></a> | 据 Bloomberg 消息称，双方已经通过一家米兰公司进行了长达数月的交涉，目前接近尾声。Pinarello 创立于 1952 年，每年的销售额超过 5000 万欧元。收购之后，Pinarello 现任 CEO  Fausto Pinarello 将继续管理该公司，本次收购被视作是 LVMH 集团进军体育界战略的一部分。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p class=\"\">上海时装周进行到第 8 天，更多英国品牌以及由英国设计师在中国创立的品牌出现在秀场。</p><p class=\"\">总部位于曼切斯特的英国女装品牌 Glamorous 今年 4 月因凯特王妃穿了该品牌一款 50 英镑的印花长裙而走红。18 日，它们第一次参加上海时装周，发布了 2017 年春夏系列，将牛仔、雪纺、纯棉混合在一起，并且加入了大量的褶皱和荷叶边。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019084956Jv6Q9yHGlmwYEeNa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499422\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019085010lZWDHgwyb6k5fMOs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498901\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019085021sF70DaqJ9ZpotzNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501104\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610190850333Gr9lkzTmpVY6PHa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500568\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">连续 4 年参加上海时装周的男装品牌 AK Club 发布了以“Evolution: from War to Peace”为主题的春夏系列，灵感来自二战老军装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090034X7WGNylnSsqxB2rw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498858\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090043G7cfIQC9TDkviudE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610190900563RnvGuH0O15WLbV4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501149\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090105wNqJZHG1sfz9UycR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499448\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090118BuM61irmhTqVUaXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Wang Feng 2017 春夏高定系列发布：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101909045014JLjewtcTYOb8Vk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090505ybWgXxslAh3FKkR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498896\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090513ZW4x03hCFfgGPSrl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090521s7xCXgydkO1RVJWQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019090530V1OQYGHCPDoMemqk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610190905412vbKRgshPBruD6Iw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499431\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">Complementair ，来源于法语“互补”，2017SS 系列作品以“逆”为主题，灵感来自世间万物相生相克，互相纠缠的复杂关系。整场秀模糊性别意识，意在构建“温柔式女权”时装。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092336Xc7UC0Vejdow6tQz.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092342Iv1t0TuJeQKP9wLC.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092342fNQlLCDPxpmhBe8O.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499567\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610190923439t2D4FAjQIWLcyYM.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500217\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092344z4I0vfPXFqNbwBsj.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092346ODmFioV16KkQbYlS.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499369\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092346kNRrOTMU3m6xScbd.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500213\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092349kjYT2xVPstpJiGg4.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019092349XgkjJBWbmDIrVAPo.JPG\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/lego-playbox-shopping-bag\" rel=\"nofollow\">LEGO 推出了积木手购物袋</a>，这是来自来自纽约视觉艺术设计学院的设计师 Junho Lee 和 Hyun Chul Choi的作品。它将拎带隐藏在购物袋内，从而制造出“积木手”的错觉，还挺有趣的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100534phRXkCvt5HOjGUdW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100542xhTFNpvC63X9OrV5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100550DgqSXREkmnMTQvZ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/vetements-x-reebok-pump-closer-look\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 与 Reebook 的联名鞋款</a>，运用了 Pump 技术，仅以黑色 logo 点缀的轻薄全白鞋面倒不像是 Vetements 一贯的张扬风格，这双鞋的定价约为 350 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100419il3SM6CZNQPwXspv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100428D6BJzaoH1OTjuyKf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100523xdJYlO4DKLqcba1i.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100444O65glSCyYMzijRIV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/10/bape-x-coca-cola-collaboration\" rel=\"nofollow\">A Bathing Ape 公布与可口可乐的全新联名系列</a>。继 2014 年之后这两大品牌再度合作，以“喝可乐的猿人”为主角，红、黑、白为主色调，带来了众多单品。该系列的定价从 2500 到 27800 日元不等，将于 10 月 22 日至 30 日在 BAPE 原宿店限定发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100451kZQgFjWiexfdavTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100500IRfolzXZr6L9sAeN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100500bwOsr97mKEZF2NQ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100500dvaQYuRK78UPHzTn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100500ktgj8HzwDFuLGMEA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100500OdNjsQJFrmvnzyS8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100500o1Ty6zdp4aSsvMNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100501XsNDcxpUI7dinFYC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161019100501PyjNGLbTFzvhsErq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666016\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610191005003UuThzLnefict1Rd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p>"}